data.Name: Northlane
data.Bio: Northlane is a djent/progressive metalcore band from Sydney, Australia. founded in 2009. The current lineup: Marcus Bridge - Vocals (2014-) Jon Deiley - Guitar (2009-) Josh Smith - Guitar (2009-) Nic Petterson - Drums (2010-) Past Members: Adrian Fitipaldes – Vocals (2009–2014) Brendan Derby – Drums (2009) Mitchell Collier – Drums (2010) Simon Anderson – Bass (2010–2011) Alex Milovic – Bass (2009-2010, 2011-2018) Brendon Padjasek - Bass/Backing Vocals (2018-2021) Read more on Last.fm
